Package org.deeplearning4j.arbiter.optimize.api

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CandidateGenerator
    A CandidateGenerator proposes candidates (i.e., hyperparameter configurations) for evaluation.
    ParameterSpace<P>
    ParameterSpace: defines the acceptable ranges of values a given parameter may take.
    TaskCreator
    The TaskCreator is used to take a candidate configuration, data provider and score function, and create something that can be executed as a Callable
